<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
		<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
		<title>{{ title }}</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../public/stylesheets/common_mobile.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../public/stylesheets/turntable.css">
		<!-- 移动端适配 -->
		<script>
			var html = document.querySelector('html');
			changeRem();
			window.addEventListener('resize', changeRem);

			function changeRem() {
				var width = html.getBoundingClientRect().width;
				html.style.fontSize = width / 10 + 'px';
			}
		</script>
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="wrap">
			<!-- <div class="caidai"></div>-->
			<div class="header clearfix">
				<p class="rule fl">规则</p>
				<a href="" id="myWin">
					<p class="my fr">我的奖品</p>
				</a>
				<div class="title"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="luckbox">
				<ul class="luck_ul">
					{% for item in lucklyList %}
					<span class="luck_span">恭喜{{item.person}}获得{{item.gift}}一份</span> {% endfor %}
				</ul>
			</div>
			<!--轮盘-->
			<div class="rotate">
				<div class="lunpai">
					<ul class="prize running">
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>iPhoneX</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>1元红包</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>10个活力果</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>80元红包</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>5个活力果</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>10元红包</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>8元红包</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>100个活力果</p>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span></span>
							<p>5元红包</p>
						</li>

					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="ring"></div>
				<div id="btn"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="border">
				您还有 <span id="change">{{ personVitality }}</span>活力果可抽奖，<span style="color:red;">每次抽奖消耗一个</span>
			</div>
			<!--<div class="border">
        
    </div>-->
			<!--滚动信息-->
			<div class="scroll">
				<p></p>
				<div>
					<ul class="personList">
						{% for item in giftList %}
						<li class="gift">
							恭喜<span class="start-num">{{item.phone}}</span> 获得
							<span class="info">{{item.gift}}</span><span>{{item.unit}}</span>
						</li>
						{% endfor %}
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!--游戏规则弹窗-->
			<div id="mask-rule">
				<div class="box-rule">
					<span class="star"></span>
					<h2>活动规则说明</h2>
					<span id="close-rule"></span>
					<div class="con">
						<div class="text">
							<p>1.本活动长期有效，参与抽奖每次消耗1个活力果，无次数限制；</p>
							<p>2.抽中的现金红包直接发放至用户账户余额，活力果和活力树券直接发放至用户活力口袋和活力果园；</p>
							<p>3.本活动公平公正公开，如恶意刷奖，一经发现将取消抽奖资格，之前抽中的所有奖品均视为无效；</p>
							<p>4.参与抽奖过程中遇到任何疑问请联系客服：0797-2131415；</p>
							<p>5.本活动最终解释权归链活团队所有。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!--中奖提示-->
			<div id="mask">
				<div class="blin"></div>
				<div class="caidai"></div>
				<div class="winning">
					<div class="red-head"></div>
					<div class="red-body"></div>
					<div id="card">
						<a href="javascript:;" target="_self" class="win"></a>
					</div>
					<a href="javascript:;" target="_self" class="btn"></a>
					<span id="close"></span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div style="position: fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.9);width:100%;height:100%;" id="main">
			<div class="main">
				<div class="loading">
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
					<span></span>
				</div>
				<p class="loading" style="color:#fff;font-size:0.4rem;margin-top:0.8rem;">努力加载中</p>
				<!--<p class="loading" style="color:#fff;font-size:0.8rem;margin-top:0.8rem;">系统修复中，待开启。。</p>-->
			</div>

		</div>

		<div id="alertBox" style="display: none;">
    		
    	</div>
		<audio src="../../public/audio/3394.mp3" id="audio"></audio>

		<script src="../../public/javascripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="../../public/javascripts/jquery.rotate.js"></script>
		<script src="../../public/javascripts/h5_game_common.js?version=1.0.0"></script>
		<script src="../../public/javascripts/turntable.js"></script>
		<script src="../../public/javascripts/md5.js"></script>
		<script src="https://cdn.bootcss.com/jsencrypt/3.0.0-beta.1/jsencrypt.min.js"></script>
	</body>

</html>